<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV37">
<l>kāyttanīḷvi ḷaṅkaṉiyu tirttetirnta pūṅkuruntañ</l>
<l>cāyttumāpi ḷantakaitta lattakaṇṇa ṉeṉparāl</l>
<l>āyccipālai yuṇṭumaṇṇai yuṇṭuveṇṇe yuṇṭupiṉ</l>
<l>pēyccipālai yuṇṭupaṇṭo rēṉamāya vāmaṉā.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Oh, they say, ‘Kṛṣṇa with hands that split open the horse,</l>
<l rend="indent">Causing the fruits of the tall, fruiting wood-apple to drop,</l>
<l>And felling the flowering wild lime that opposed [Him]!’</l>
<l>O Vāmana, who—drinking the cowherdess’s milk, swallowing the earth,</l>
<l rend="indent">Eating butter, and drinking the demoness’s milk—</l>
<l>became a boar in the past!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
